    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    BookingCalendarPanel
    Calendar panel for displaying property availability during booking process.
    BookingMenuGUI
    GUI dialog for booking management operations.
    CalendarGridPanel
    Interactive calendar grid panel that displays property dates.
    CreatePropertyDialog
    Dialog for creating a new property in the system.
    Date
    The Date class represents a specific day of a month in a property's availability calendar.
    DateEditDialog
    Dialog for editing a specific date's price and environmental rate.
    EnvironmentalRatesDialog
    Dialog for managing environmental rates across property dates.
    MainFrame
    The main window for the Green Property Exchange System GUI.
    ManagePropertyDialog
    Dialog for managing a property's settings and details.
    Property
    Represents a property with a name, type, available dates, and reservations.
    PropertyMenuGUI
    GUI dialog for property management operations.
    PropertySystem
    The PropertySystem class stores all properties and their reservations.
    PropertyType
    Enumerates the available property types and their price multipliers.
    Reservation
    Represents a reservation made by a guest.
    SimulateBookingDialog
    Dialog for simulating a new booking with calendar view.
    ViewPropertyDialog
    Dialog for viewing comprehensive property information.
    ViewReservationsDialog
    Dialog for viewing all reservations for a specific property.
